{"tid":2314820,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"大公司轉細公司","createTime":"2020-12-06T19:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T07:53:24.000Z","uid":381965,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"73c4d99ba8e6a7c6503d3e1dd4d88cab0b06b917","tid":2314820,"uid":381965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T19:44:32.000Z","msg":"之前裸辭左，而家咁嘅時勢有啲難搵工，想做番大公司但又唔想調低個人工<br />\n假設舊公司係出名嘅公司<br />\n以前啲工作經驗都傾向係中至大公司<br />\n如果而家有間唔出名公司出offer，basic會高過以前大概兩成，但overall未必高好多，做唔做好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb074aa433b473a9eec0e8dc126b85abb661f12","tid":2314820,"uid":44854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T19:48:52.000Z","msg":"再簡下先"},{"pid":"fc42eeca219e8fc7fd82a209c275ab0600c118eb","tid":2314820,"uid":381965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6cb074aa433b473a9eec0e8dc126b85abb661f12","tid":2314820,"uid":44854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T19:48:52.000Z","msg":"再簡下先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T19:56:11.000Z","msg":"我都想，但搵工搵到少少絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce0cf017d94f1e658b03c74689812a433409c4a","tid":2314820,"uid":44504,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T20:40:29.000Z","msg":"有得揀你就唔會問 <br />\n接受現實啦"},{"pid":"cdfd0e12b8665f0f9a789adf80e11b379f980d14","tid":2314820,"uid":283887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc42eeca219e8fc7fd82a209c275ab0600c118eb","tid":2314820,"uid":381965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6cb074aa433b473a9eec0e8dc126b85abb661f12","tid":2314820,"uid":44854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T19:48:52.000Z","msg":"再簡下先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T19:56:11.000Z","msg":"我都想，但搵工搵到少少絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T21:06:12.000Z","msg":"搵左幾耐呀？申請左幾多份？"},{"pid":"fc77d8f75919afec3e3c3bc6c03d